data.description: A classic early 1900's home in great condition just minutes from downtown, hospitals, Union Park, and much more.  The house is a perfect family home or great investment property.  Newly refinished original hardwood floors throughout main level and second floor.  Newer LVP flooring in kitchen, laundry, and both bathrooms.  Brand new efficient windows on second floor.  Modern bathroom with tile shower.  Brand new 1/2 bath added to main floor.  Don't miss your opportunity to get into a move in ready home at this price point.
